items.name: Smart-Surveillance-System

items.description: A multi-model pipeline integrating LLM and voice processing that creates a fully voice-controlled LLM. The program utilizes state-of-the-art LLMs, TTS models, STT models, and VAD, resulting in a responsive voice assistant capable of fluid conversation with users.
